.TH tftp_logger 3 "tftp 1.2.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
tftp_logger \- Trivial FTP logger.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
A \fItftp_logger\fR callback module is to be implemented as a \fItftp_logger\fR behavior and export the following functions:

.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
.SH CALLBACKS
.LP
.B
\fBerror_msg(Format, Args)\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Logs an error message. See \fIlogger:error/2\fR for details.


.RE
.B
\fBinfo_msg(Format, Args)\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Logs an info message. See \fIlogger:info/2\fR for details.


.RE
.B
\fBwarning_msg(Format, Args)\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Logs a warning message. See \fIlogger:warning/2\fR for details.


.RE
